data.description:
Beautiful 2 story home in the heart of Indianola. Walking distance to Simpson College!
Easy access to the highway, close to the Grocery store and a park right down the street.
Historic and beautiful woodwork with updated kitchen with darling breakfast nook. Check out the original beautiful hardwood floors! South facing porch for relaxing on these comfortable fall days. Nice sized 2-car garage with cute courtyard, perfect for entertaining in the backyard.
Three comfortable bedrooms upstairs with updated bathroom upstairs. Unfinished attic for storage or kids' playroom. Warm and rustic finished basement with laundry and 3/4 bathroom. Perfect for the man cave or the craft​​‌​​​​‌​‌​​​‌​​​​‌‌​​​​​​‌‌​​​​ room!
